snippet.title: Adventure Kitty: Drill Buster | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait is almost over!
Adventure Kitty: Drill Buster will be released September 2, 2022 on itch.io!

Go for gold and test your risk/reward skills in Adventure Kitty: Drill Buster!
An action paced drill game that has you drilling across new terrains and adapting from your original plan.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/ZaltickGames
Website: https://drill-buster-site.vercel.app/
TIkTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@zaltickgames
